_sText:
Pistol spawns random jail every round.
Doors open 1 min after spawn.

So after CS:S update I decided to fix 418 missing textures in my map, however I edited map even more and now its more like remake. I did not add anything big just 1 secret and few new areas, and 1 extra vent.

I may or may not release later the old version with fixed textures.

I hope this is the final, but If you have some suggestions, I would like to hear them.

Old version: http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/64389
